Product Name: Pep Nails Luxury Press On Nails Kit (Drop Dead Gorgeous)
Usage Instructions:
How to apply?

1. Find your sizes.
2. Remove any polish from your nails.
3. Push your cuticles back.
4. Sanitise with alcohol swabs.
5. Buff your natural nails with the nail filer.
6. Apply glue tabs or glue carefully.
7. Stick the nails, press for 30 seconds and done!
8. If required, cut, file and shape as per your liking.

How to remove?

1. Soak in warm soapy water for 10-20 minutes.
2. Remove the pep nails using the sloping edge of the cuticle stick.
3. Pat your hands dry.
4. Gently, buff off the glue with the nail filer or the nail buffer.
5. Lastly, follow all the steps on pep four way nail buffer for glossy nails.

(For detailed instructions please check the instructions manual provided in the box).
Special Features:
Half the cost of salon nails.
Reusable upto 4 to 5 times.
Stays upto 2-3 weeks.
24 nails to ensure perfect and natural fit.
Apply and remove in 10 minutes.
Absolutely non damaging.

Ps: Pep Nails will make your hands look delicious!
